00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:44.800
Oke.

00:14:48.880 --> 00:14:50.320
Salam, Pak.

00:14:50.440 --> 00:14:52.920
Tadi malam, beberapa
anak berpesta di hotel Anda.

00:14:53.400 --> 00:14:55.320
Anak-anak saya termasuk di antara mereka.

00:14:55.960 --> 00:14:59.040
Saya ingin melihat rekaman
CCTV pesta jika Anda mengizinkan.

00:14:59.120 --> 00:15:01.440
